originalText.text: This management office is horrible. They are so rude, unorganized and unprofessional. I am in the process of moving into one of their buildings and Nadiesha James as well as some other employees there have made this process a complete nightmare. They have mixed up my paperwork several times, they’ve LOST my papers several times; important PII (including my social security and bank statements). Then when you will not tolerate such incompetence and complain they come at you with an attitude for standing up for yourself and making sure your personal documents are safe. Nadiesha James actually lied and said she sent me my lease when in fact she knew she made a mistake on her end and sent it to someone else’s email for the 2nd time. Instead of taking accountability she would rather go back and forth and try and make the client seem like a liar. They seriously need to revise their staff because the poor customer service is reflecting on the company and the beautiful buildings being constructed.
